beer.beer_description:
The original sloth: a hopped up American Pale Ale.

Single hopped with Galaxy.

A malty backbone for a pale ale with notes of caramel and biscuit. 

The Galaxy hop shines with an assertive bitterness and big passionfruit aromas.
